title: We four.
author: Rees, L. L.
snippet: To the left of this group is Liberty, guarding these illustrious sons, such as Malesherbes, Mirabeau,  Monge, Fenelon, Manuel, and Carnot, the leader in the first Kevolution, Berthollet, and Laplace, with David, Bichat, Lafliyette, Cuvier, Voltaire, and Rousseau.
